{"id":14564,"date":"2023-08-10T09:02:04","date_gmt":"2023-08-10T02:02:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=14564"},"modified":"2023-08-11T08:49:21","modified_gmt":"2023-08-11T01:49:21","slug":"hyundai-hai-phong-trien-khai-chuong-trinh-uu-dai-thang-8-don-thu-sang-ngan-uu-dai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-hai-phong-trien-khai-chuong-trinh-uu-dai-thang-8-don-thu-sang-ngan-uu-dai\/","title":{"rendered":"Hyundai H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i th\u00e1ng 8 &#8220;\u0110\u00f3n thu sang &#8211; Ng\u00e0n \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i&#8221;"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1eeb nay cho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft 31\/08\/2023, Hyundai H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u201c\u0110\u00f3n thu sang &#8211; Ng\u00e0n \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i\u201d<\/p>\n<p>M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 qua, v\u00e0 m\u00f9a thu \u0111ang t\u1edbi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1eafc m\u00e0u r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, n\u0103m h\u1ecdc m\u1edbi c\u0169ng s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn, nhi\u1ec1u b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n gi\u00fap \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u00f3n con em m\u00ecnh an to\u00e0n, tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi m\u01b0a n\u1eafng th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft. V\u00ec v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe \u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u00e0m ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n di chuy\u1ec3n cho c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, nh\u00f3m b\u1ea1n \u01b0a kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 hay ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u00f4ng minh, thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng l\u01b0a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1ea5t trong d\u1ecbp n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1\/7\/2023 cho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft 31\/12\/2023, ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ebfn 50% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u00f4 t\u00f4 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1edbm th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-hai-phong-trien-khai-chuong-trinh-uu-dai-thang-8-don-thu-sang-ngan-uu-dai\/z4590439375404_80ed3e2fde395e20f593e09af6fe237c\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-14565\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-14565\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/z4590439375404_80ed3e2fde395e20f593e09af6fe237c-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/z4590439375404_80ed3e2fde395e20f593e09af6fe237c-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/z4590439375404_80ed3e2fde395e20f593e09af6fe237c-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/z4590439375404_80ed3e2fde395e20f593e09af6fe237c-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/z4590439375404_80ed3e2fde395e20f593e09af6fe237c-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/z4590439375404_80ed3e2fde395e20f593e09af6fe237c.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ebfc xe ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, ti\u1ec7n nghi v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i cho c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh, HTV ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u201c\u0110\u00f3n thu sang &#8211; Ng\u00e0n \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i\u201d \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y 31\/08\/2023 t\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd \u1ee7y quy\u1ec1n Hyundai tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n<p>Theo \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edfng 1 trong 2 g\u00f3i \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t:<\/p>\n<p>G\u00f3i 1: \u01afu \u0111\u00e3i l\u00e3i su\u1ea5t tr\u1ea3 g\u00f3p ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 0-4,2% trong 12 th\u00e1ng (\u00c2n h\u1ea1n n\u1ee3 g\u1ed1c t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c t\u1eebng ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng)<\/p>\n<p>G\u00f3i 2: G\u00f3i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00f9ng qu\u00e0 t\u1eb7ng khi mua xe Hyundai. Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eadn th\u00eam \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i tr\u1ea3 g\u00f3p l\u00e3i su\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eadn ngay qu\u00e0 t\u1eb7ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u1eeb Hyundai (G\u00f3i b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t 1 n\u0103m ho\u1eb7c 01 camera h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh cao c\u1ea5p) \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u vay tr\u1ea3 g\u00f3p.<\/p>\n<p>Trong \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ee9c l\u00e3i su\u1ea5t \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vay mua xe t\u1ea1i Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Ngo\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VCB). Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c T\u1ebf Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VIB), \u00a0Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng TMCP X\u0103ng d\u1ea7u Petrolimex (PG Bank) v\u00e0 Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Vi\u1ec7t Nam Th\u1ecbnh V\u01b0\u1ee3ng (VPB).<\/p>\n<p>Chi ti\u1ebft \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe, c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng. Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i.<\/p>\n<div class=\"block-date\">\n<div class=\"chat-item flx \">\n<div class=\"chat-content flx flx-col flx-cell\">\n<div id=\"bb_msg_id_1691056320621\" class=\"chat-message wrap-message rotate-container -send-time -reaction\" data-node-type=\"bubble-message\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<div class=\"card last-msg card--text\" data-id=\"div_ReceivedMsg_Text\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"card-send-time flx flx-al-c flx-1 preview-ts__first-msg\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"message-reaction-container has-send-time show-react-btn\">\n<div data-id=\"btn_ReceivedMsg_React\">\n<div class=\"msg-reaction-icon\">\n<div class=\"default-react-icon-thumb\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"emoji-list-wrapper hide-elist\">\n<div class=\"reaction-emoji-list \">\n<div class=\"reaction-emoji-icon\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"reaction-emoji-icon\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"reaction-emoji-icon\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"reaction-emoji-icon\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"reaction-emoji-icon\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"reaction-emoji-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"chat-message__actionholder last-msg\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"block-date\">\n<div class=\"chat-item flx \">\n<div class=\"rel zavatar-container avatar--overlay\">\n<div class=\"zavatar zavatar-m zavatar-single flx flx-al-c flx-center rel clickable disableDrag\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"chat-content flx flx-col flx-cell\">\n<div id=\"bb_msg_id_1691121816855\" class=\"chat-message wrap-message rotate-container -send-time -reaction\" data-node-type=\"bubble-message\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<div class=\"card card--link\" data-id=\"div_ReceivedMsg_Link\">\n<div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1eeb nay cho \u0111\u1ebf